It is used to display information related to mounted file systems about total space and available space.
It displays the space available on all currently mounted file systems.

$ df --help
$ df
$ df -a
$ df -h
$ df -T
$ df -Th
$ df -aTh
$ df --total
$ df /FOLDER_NAME
$ df -h /FOLDER_NAME
$ df -H /FOLDER_NAME
$ df -T /FOLDER_NAME
